### Listar productos
GET http://localhost:8081/api/productos
Accept: application/json

# Nota: el backend no expone endpoints /favorites. Las llamadas de frontend a favoritos se limpian devolviendo lista vacía.

### Crear producto
POST http://localhost:8081/api/productos
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juego demo",
  "descripcion": "Descripción",
  "imagen": "https://example.com/demo.jpg",
  "precio": 19990,
  "valoracion": 4.2,
  "stock": 5,
  "rawgGameId": 12345
}

### Obtener producto por id
GET http://localhost:8081/api/productos/1
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar producto
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/productos/1
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "nombre": "Juego demo editado",
  "descripcion": "Descripción",
  "imagen": "https://example.com/demo.jpg",
  "precio": 20990,
  "valoracion": 4.3,
  "stock": 8,
  "rawgGameId": 12345
}

### Eliminar producto
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/productos/1
Accept: application/json

### Cargar keys para un producto
POST http://localhost:8081/api/keys/cargar
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 3
}

### Crear compra
POST http://localhost:8081/api/compras
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buyerName": "Ana Perez",
  "buyerEmail": "ana@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "productoId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### Obtener compra por id
GET http://localhost:8081/api/compras/1
Accept: application/json

### Importar desde RAWG (crea o actualiza por rawgId)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/productos/import/rawg/326242
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "precio": 34990,
  "stock": 5
}

### Importar página de RAWG (bulk)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/productos/import/rawg?page=1&pageSize=10&precio=29990&stock=5
Accept: application/json

### Compra usando rawgGameId (cuando no sabes el id interno)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/compras
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buyerName": "Cliente RAWG",
  "buyerEmail": "cliente@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "rawgGameId": 326242, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}
